      <title>工党的税收计划打击企业高管信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/uk-economy-business-chiefs-are-sour-on-labour-s-tax-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心新工党政府可能增加税收，企业老板对英国经济的乐观情绪在八月份大幅下降。]]></description>
