      <title>美国就业数据将帮助美联储衡量其宽松程度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/economy-week-us-jobs-data-likely-to-reflect-labor-market-moderation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将发布的美国劳动力市场数据，包括月度就业报告，将使美联储政策制定者了解在两周多一点时间几乎肯定会降息之后进一步降息的必要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/economy-week-us-jobs-data-likely-to-reflect-labor-market-moderation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>房东面临 1.5 万亿美元的商业房地产到期障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/landlords-face-a-1-5-trillion-commercial-real-estate-maturity-wall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[仲量联行表示，到明年年底，写字楼、公寓大楼和其他商业房地产的业主将有 1.5 万亿美元的债务到期，其中约四分之一的借款可能难以再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/landlords-face-a-1-5-trillion-commercial-real-estate-maturity-wall</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>圭亚那因石油产量激增将经济增长预期上调至 43%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/guyana-raises-yearly-growth-estimates-to-42-8-from-34-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统伊尔凡·阿里将圭亚那年经济增长预期从之前的 34.8% 上调至 42.8%，因为他预计公共和私营部门的投资将“增加”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/guyana-raises-yearly-growth-estimates-to-42-8-from-34-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 17:19:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非财政部长称稳定的政治环境有利于兰特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/south-african-finance-minister-says-stable-politics-buoying-rand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长埃诺克·戈东瓦纳 (Enoch Godongwana) 表示，南非 5 月份大选后迅速组建新联合政府，增强了投资者信心，推动了南非货币和股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/south-african-finance-minister-says-stable-politics-buoying-rand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 15:17:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国钢铁行业领导者对 2025 年复苏寄予厚望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/us-steel-industry-sees-economy-reviving-demand-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国钢铁业高管表示，他们乐观地认为，明年对这种工业材料的需求将会反弹，从2024年困扰该行业的需求低迷和低价中恢复过来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/us-steel-industry-sees-economy-reviving-demand-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度预计下月季风降雨充沛，农作物长势良好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/india-predicts-ample-monsoon-rain-next-month-in-boost-to-crops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据预测，印度六月至九月季风季节的最后一个月降雨量将高于正常水平，为水稻和大豆等作物的丰收带来光明的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/india-predicts-ample-monsoon-rain-next-month-in-boost-to-crops</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 12:26:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒂森克虏伯钢铁公司前董事会主席称将从克雷廷斯基获利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/thyssenkrupp-steel-to-profit-from-kretinsky-ex-board-head-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒂森克虏伯股份公司陷入困境的钢铁部门将因捷克亿万富翁丹尼尔·克雷廷斯基的深入参与而获益，该部门即将离任的监事会主席西格玛·加布里尔 (Sigmar Gabriel) 向《明镜周刊》表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/thyssenkrupp-steel-to-profit-from-kretinsky-ex-board-head-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 10:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
